node.text:
INGREDIENTS
Pizza Dough:
* 	¾ cup lukewarm water
* 	1 ½ packets yeast
* 	¾ cup water
* 	3 tbsp oil
* 	3 tbsp honey
* 	½ tsp salt
* 	4 ½ cups bread flour
Chicken Alfredo Mix: 
* 	2 tbsp butter
* 	3 cloves garlic, minced 
* 	2 cups heavy cream
* 	½ cup finely grated parmesan 
* 	3 chicken breasts, cooked and seasoned
* 	1 cup grated mozzarella
* 	1 cup ricotta 
* 	8 rashers bacon, cooked crispy and chopped 
* 	2 tbsp finely chopped parsley
 
Tomato Sauce: 
* 	2 tsp oil
* 	1 clove garlic, minced
* 	½ stp chili flakes
* 	2 cups passata
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
Pizza
* 	Sliced pepperoni
* 	Mozzarella
* 	Garlic butter

node.text:
Make it for your friends this weekend!
INGREDIENTS
Taco Mix:
2 tsp oil
½ onion, diced
400g beef mince
2 garlic cloves, minced
1 tsp cumin powder
1 tsp paprika
1 tsp chili powder
¼ cup salsa
Salt and pepper to taste
Chicken Fajita:
2 tsp oil
½ onion, diced
1 cup diced mixed peppers
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 chicken breasts, cooked, shredded
2 tbsp tomato paste
2 tbsp water
Steak Fajita:
½ onion, sliced
1 cup sliced mixed peppers
2 rump steaks, thinly sliced
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 tsp lime juice
Guacamole:
3 ripe avocados
1 small red onion, finely chopped
1 tbsp finely chopped coriander
½ tsp cumin powder
¼ tsp chilli powder
Juice of 2 limes
Salt and pepper to taste
8 large tortilla wraps
Sliced mozzarella
1 cups Grated cheddar cheese
1 cup grated mixed cheddar
Salsa
Sour Cream

node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
* 	½ red chilli, finely chopped
* 	½ tsp Dijon
* 	3 tbsp Red wine vinegar 
* 	2 tbsp Olive oil 
* 	1 Anchovy
 
Artichoke Aioli
* 	1 egg yolk
* 	1 garlic clove
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
* 	Pinch salt
* 	2 artichoke hearts 
* 	1 lemon, juiced
* 	Vegetable oil - around 100ml
 
To serve
* 	Thick white bread

CROQUE MONSIEUR MASH BALLS
INGREDIENTS
* 6 cups cold leftover mash
* 4 slices ham, chopped into small cubes
* 3 cups grated emmental
* 2 tbsp dijon mustard
* 1/4 cup finely chopped parsley
* 1 tbsp salt
* 1 tbsp pepper
* 1 cup flour
* 4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* Enough groundnut oil to deep fry

Make it for your friends this weekend!
INGREDIENTS
Taco Mix:
2 tsp oil
½ onion, diced
400g beef mince
2 garlic cloves, minced
1 tsp cumin powder
1 tsp paprika
1 tsp chili powder
¼ cup salsa
Salt and pepper to taste
Chicken Fajita:
2 tsp oil
½ onion, diced
1 cup diced mixed peppers
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 chicken breasts, cooked, shredded
2 tbsp tomato paste
2 tbsp water
Steak Fajita:
½ onion, sliced
1 cup sliced mixed peppers
2 rump steaks, thinly sliced
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 tsp lime juice
Guacamole:
3 ripe avocados
1 small red onion, finely chopped
1 tbsp finely chopped coriander
½ tsp cumin powder
¼ tsp chilli powder
Juice of 2 limes
Salt and pepper to taste
8 large tortilla wraps
Sliced mozzarella
1 cups Grated cheddar cheese
1 cup grated mixed cheddar
Salsa
Sour Cream

node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
* 	½ red chilli, finely chopped
* 	½ tsp Dijon
* 	3 tbsp Red wine vinegar 
* 	2 tbsp Olive oil 
* 	1 Anchovy
 
Artichoke Aioli
* 	1 egg yolk
* 	1 garlic clove
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
* 	Pinch salt
* 	2 artichoke hearts 
* 	1 lemon, juiced
* 	Vegetable oil - around 100ml
 
To serve
* 	Thick white bread 

#fschnitzel #foodpics #foodphotography #foodgram #foodlovers #fooddiary #foodforthought #sandwich #eeeeeats #cheesetoastie #noleftovers #foodgasm

Good news Gravy lovers - Gravy season is back! 

Cheesy beef loaded fries
Ingredients
* 1 tbsp oil
* 2.2 lb sirloin steak, cut into thin strips
* 3 tbsp flour
* 1 tbsp salt
* 1 tbsp pepper
* 1 onion, sliced roughly
* 1 tbsp tomato puree
* 2 cups beef stock
* 1 cup wine
* Thyme

HOT ROAST CHICKEN GRAVY BUNS
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 small chicken
* 	1/2 lemon
* 	1/2 bulb garlic
* 	1 1/2 tsps salt
* 	1 cup mayonnaise
* 	toasted buns, to serve
* 	1 cup chicken stock
* 	fries, to serve
* 	1 glass white wine
* 	1 tbsp french mustard
* 	1 hpd tsp plain flour

GRAVY AND MASH BOMBS
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 cup/250ml gravy
* 	3 cups/1 kilo pork mince
* 	1 tbsp chopped chives
* 	2 tbsp chopped parsley
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1 tsp pepper
* 	1 tsp nutmeg
* 	2 cups mashed potato
* 	1 cup plain flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 	2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* 	Groundnut oil for deep frying

Cheese stuffed mash beef Pie

* 2 1/4 lb Stewing beef
* 2 cloves Garlic
* 2 Onions
* 1 1/2 cups Beef stock
* 3 tbsp Flour
* 2 tsp Pepper
* 2 tsp Salt
* 1 tbsp Vegetable oil
* 1 tbsp Butter
* 1 small block Cheddar
* 2 cups Red wine
* 3 cups Leftover mash
* 1 tbsp Passasta

#twistedfood #recipe #pie #mash  #gravy #gravytrain #yummy #dinnerideas #nowimhungry

node.text:
Comfort in a bowl - a BREAD bowl! 🍞 
Spaghetti Meatball Soup in a Garlic Bread Bowl - Come and Spaghet it 🍝 

INGREDIENTS
Spaghetti Meatball Soup Bowls
Meatballs:
400g Beef Mince
300g Pork Mince
½ cup bread crumbs
1 egg, whisked
2 cloves garlic, minced
2 tbsp chopped parsley
¼ cup finely grated parmesan
½ tsp oregano
½ tsp salt
½ tsp pepper
Diced yellow cheddar
Oil
 
3 tsp oil
1 white onion, diced
2 cloves garlic, minced
½ tsp chilli flakes
1 tsp oregano
1 tbsp tomato paste
600ml passata
4 cups chicken stock
2 cups water
½ tsp salt
½ tsp pepper
225g dry spaghetti
 
Large sourdough boule

•
#bread #breadbowl #comfortfood #meatballs #spaghetti #goodsoup #goodrecipe #autumn #autumnrecipe
